// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1515 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e5501ffe-54aa-5dd7-a759-3c81b4ed010d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:17.04*")
